---
<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} canonical={canonical} og={og} schema={schema} active={active}>
<!-- ═══ HERO ═══ -->
  <section class="hero" style="min-height:auto;padding:160px 0 80px;">
    <div class="hero__bg-gradient"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero__content reveal" style="--delay:0;max-width:800px;">
        <div class="hero__pre-label">
          <span class="hero__dot"></span>
          Licensed &amp; Insured • 30+ Years
        </div>
        <h1>Pest Control in LaVerkin, Utah<br><span>Zion Corridor Protection</span></h1>

        <!-- ═══ SEO: AI SUMMARY BLOCK ═══ -->
        <p>Wernex Termite &amp; Pest Control provides licensed pest control in LaVerkin, Utah — a key community in the Zion Corridor between Hurricane and Toquerville. LaVerkin's warm microclimate along the Virgin River creates year-round pest activity including ants, spiders, scorpions, and rodents. Backed by 30+ years of <a href="pest-control-southern-utah.html">Southern Utah pest control</a> experience, Wernex offers same-day inspections, eco-friendly IPM treatments, quarterly protection plans, and a 100% satisfaction guarantee. Call (435) 673-9503.</p>

        <div class="hero__buttons" style="margin-top:28px;">
          <a href="contact.html" class="btn btn--primary">Get a Free Quote →</a>
          <a href="tel:+14356739503" class="btn btn--white">📞 (435) 673-9503</a>
        </div>
        <div class="hero__badges" style="margin-top:24px;">
          <div class="hero__badge"><div class="hero__badge-icon">✓</div><span>Licensed &amp; Insured</span></div>
          <div class="hero__badge"><div class="hero__badge-icon">🌿</div><span>Eco-Friendly</span></div>
          <div class="hero__badge"><div class="hero__badge-icon">⏱️</div><span>Same-Day Service</span></div>
          <div class="hero__badge"><div class="hero__badge-icon">🔒</div><span>Satisfaction Guaranteed</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center reveal">
          <span class="section-label">LaVerkin Pest Challenges</span>
          <h2>Zion Corridor Homes Face Year-Round Pest Pressure</h2>
          <p class="mx-auto" style="margin-top:12px;color:var(--gray);">LaVerkin's position along the Virgin River between Hurricane and Zion National Park creates a natural pest corridor. Desert terrain, irrigated yards, and river moisture combine to sustain ant colonies, spider populations, scorpions, and rodent activity across all four seasons.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(280px,1fr));gap:24px;margin-top:48px;">
          <div class="card reveal"><div class="card__body"><h3>🐜 Ant Colonies</h3><p style="color:var(--gray);">Fire ants and pavement ants are prolific in LaVerkin yards. Hot summers drive them indoors seeking water and food, leading to kitchen and bathroom invasions.</p></div></div>
          <div class="card reveal"><div class="card__body"><h3>🕷️ Black Widows</h3><p style="color:var(--gray);">LaVerkin garages, sheds, and outdoor furniture harbor black widows. The warm microclimate supports active spider populations from early spring through late fall.</p></div></div>
          <div class="card reveal"><div class="card__body"><h3>🏡 Vacation Rental Pests</h3><p style="color:var(--gray);">LaVerkin's growing vacation rental market near Zion means guest complaints about pests can tank your reviews. Wernex offers turnover-scheduled treatments to keep properties guest-ready.</p></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section--dark section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="stats-bar">
          <div class="stat reveal"><div class="stat__number">30+</div><div class="stat__label">Years in Southern Utah</div></div>
          <div class="stat reveal"><div class="stat__number">4.9★</div><div class="stat__label">Google Rating</div></div>
          <div class="stat reveal"><div class="stat__number">Same Day</div><div class="stat__label">LaVerkin Service</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center reveal"><span class="section-label">Zion Corridor</span><h2>Nearby Service Areas</h2></div>
        <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:16px;margin-top:32px;">
          <a href="pest-control-hurricane-ut.html" class="btn btn--outline" style="text-align:center;">📍 Hurricane</a>
          <a href="pest-control-near-zion-national-park.html" class="btn btn--outline" style="text-align:center;">📍 Near Zion</a>
          <a href="best-pest-control-st-george.html" class="btn btn--outline" style="text-align:center;">📍 St. George</a>
          <a href="pest-control-southern-utah.html" class="btn btn--outline" style="text-align:center;">🛡️ All Southern Utah</a>
          <a href="pest-control-vacation-rentals-southern-utah.html" class="btn btn--outline" style="text-align:center;">🏡 Vacation Rental Service</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ FAQ SECTION ═══ -->
    <section class="section--alt section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center reveal">
          <span class="section-label">Common Questions</span>
          <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        </div>
        <div style="max-width:800px;margin:40px auto 0;">

        <details class="reveal" style="background:var(--off-white);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:20px 24px;margin-bottom:12px;cursor:pointer;">
          <summary style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--text-dark);">Does Wernex serve LaVerkin, Utah?</summary>
          <p style="margin-top:12px;color:var(--text-body);max-width:65ch;">Yes. LaVerkin is within our primary service area along the Zion Corridor. We provide same-day pest control service to LaVerkin homes and businesses. Call (435) 673-9503.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="reveal" style="background:var(--off-white);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:20px 24px;margin-bottom:12px;cursor:pointer;">
          <summary style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--text-dark);">What pests are common in LaVerkin?</summary>
          <p style="margin-top:12px;color:var(--text-body);max-width:65ch;">Ants, black widow spiders, bark scorpions, and mice are the most common pests in LaVerkin. The Virgin River corridor and surrounding desert terrain support active pest populations year-round.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="reveal" style="background:var(--off-white);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:20px 24px;margin-bottom:12px;cursor:pointer;">
          <summary style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--text-dark);">Does Wernex also service vacation rentals in LaVerkin?</summary>
          <p style="margin-top:12px;color:var(--text-body);max-width:65ch;">Yes. We provide pest management programs specifically designed for Airbnb and VRBO hosts in the Zion Corridor, including LaVerkin, Toquerville, Virgin, and Springdale. Scheduled treatments between guest turnovers keep properties pest-free.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="reveal" style="background:var(--off-white);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:20px 24px;margin-bottom:12px;cursor:pointer;">
          <summary style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--text-dark);">How much does pest control cost in LaVerkin?</summary>
          <p style="margin-top:12px;color:var(--text-body);max-width:65ch;">Pricing depends on the service needed and property size. We offer free inspections and competitive pricing. Quarterly protection plans provide the best value for year-round coverage. Call (435) 673-9503 for a free quote.</p>
        </details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ CTA SECTION ═══ -->
    <section class="section--dark section">
      <div class="container text-center">
